                    </div>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4 py-3 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-r-lg">
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Mid-Career — ₹15 Lakh Salary</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1"><strong>Old Regime Tax:</strong> ₹1,56,000 (with ₹1.5L 80C + ₹50K 80D + ₹2L HRA)</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><strong>New Regime Tax:</strong> ₹93,600</p>
                        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-600 mt-1"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-1"></i>Winner: New Regime saves ₹62,400</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4 py-3 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-r-lg">
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Senior Professional — ₹30 Lakh Salary (Heavy Deductions)</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1"><strong>Old Regime Tax:</strong> ₹4,26,400 (₹1.5L 80C + ₹75K 80D + ₹3L HRA + ₹2L Sec 24 + ₹50K NPS)</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"><strong>New Regime Tax:</strong> ₹4,42,000</p>
